name: Leo Aya
description: I was raised on a ship, My Uncle was a merchant marine captain, who sailed around the world, I majored in Marine engineering, I am a very outgoing, energetic person, who likes to work hard and play hard. I also enjoy relaxing, watching a sunset, moonrise, movie, sports, or a concert. I consider myself eclectic, and open minded about checking new stuff out – always trying to broaden my horizons. I especially love the outdoors – hiking, biking, camping, but do enjoy indoor activities too. I love to cook or dine out. Eating is one of my favorite pastimes.
